sentences: From 1976 to 1977 he performed with Amapola Cabase in San Francisco, California.
From 1980 to 1981, he was a sideman for Richie Cole on tour.
Enriquez became a born-again Christian in 1993 and spoke of how God had changed his life.
He died of a pulmonary embolism on August 6, 1996 in Stayton, Oregon.

sentences: Roberto Delprado Yulo "Bobby" Enriquez (May 20, 1943 – August 6, 1996) was a jazz pianist from the Philippines.
He started his professional career as a musician at the age of 14, sneaking out of his second floor bedroom window at night to play gigs.
During the next four years he made several albums for GNP Crescendo.
